{"tid":585437,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明「新女」Wing起底 傳喺公司擺款「扮代表」","createTime":"2018-03-08T15:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T04:12:56.000Z","uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51a11108e64265050cb77d30203a290c8b316a56","tid":585437,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"現年51歲嘅黎明同樂基兒離婚6年，隨着樂基兒再婚，黎明多年嚟都係緋聞絕緣，今日有周刊爆料指做咗6年鑽石筍盤嘅黎明，對32歲失婚女助手Wing照顧有加，仲話Wing已進駐黎明6千呎大宅，成功埋黎明身，譜出「父女戀」(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Fqdv5J\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Fqdv5J&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSW3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=8ad11d70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Fqdv5J</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n不過有知情人向《蘋果》爆料，指Wing一向是「進取型」，早於黎明經理人陳善之離職，經理人部門處於「真空期」，趁機「佔領」經理人部門，又指Wing以為成功上位，取代陳善之，喺公司經常指手劃腳，令同事頗有微言，但大家多一事不如少一事，一直冇向黎明透露，惟早前有員工因事被炒，故大家早料到會有負面新聞傳出。<br />\n<br />\n知情者又指寰亞最近大裁員，A Music雖然多年來由黎明掌舵，林建岳給予黎明極大自由度，但這次裁員行動，與黎明合作多年、在A Music任行政總裁，人工極高嘅王凱文亦不倖免，上月農曆年後被裁走，令Wing喺公司勢力越嚟越大。<br />\n<br />\n另，周刊報道指Wing經常出入黎明上水豪宅，據爆料人向《蘋果》稱，Leon一向鍾意叫同事去佢上水豪宅，食住早餐開會，等大家輕鬆啲，但有人因為冇車，經常往返公司同上水好唔方便，故Leon就叫佢攞公司車用。<br />\n<br />\n講到阿Wing忽然升呢一事，據知Wing喺A Music做助手嗰陣，有傳Wing當年愛李治廷，為咗佢同老公離婚，以為李治廷離開黎明公司會帶埋佢走，可惜李治廷最後戀范冰冰，離開A Music亦冇帶佢走，呢個如意算盤打唔響。<br />\n<br />\n知情者又稱，李治廷離開後，Wing試過搵工，但未搵到，咁啱A Music嗰時走好多人，Wing即有機會埋黎明身，負責對客戶嘅工作，更向外間稱，如果大家想搵黎明，可以搵佢，儼如黎明經理人，但黎明貼身助手，其實仍然係子泉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/235450_0ea8b04a41bd3b77c653e6400d844ab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F235450_0ea8b04a41bd3b77c653e6400d844ab4.jpg&h=45b82235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f74a8f7b022318d011aca347c562ff1c8b8054a9","tid":585437,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:57:47.000Z","msg":"Amusic仲有咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58de12df1ab85195a9d74f51dc2fc468a19a4d6f","tid":585437,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"又追李治廷, 又埋黎明堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6e115858f1651ce2c7ee9a75dc49ab8011b968","tid":585437,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"就咁睇張相<br />\n雖然三十幾歲人，但係個樣好似幾正"},{"pid":"a908b6b958343646fa4e5a74b5798f0d872462a6","tid":585437,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6e115858f1651ce2c7ee9a75dc49ab8011b968","tid":585437,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"就咁睇張相<br />\n雖然三十幾歲人，但係個樣好似幾正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"我屌"},{"pid":"5ac6a4a1d9e86214b7219b02c3b2b5c46856a195","tid":585437,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a908b6b958343646fa4e5a74b5798f0d872462a6","tid":585437,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6e115858f1651ce2c7ee9a75dc49ab8011b968","tid":585437,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"就咁睇張相<br />\n雖然三十幾歲人，但係個樣好似幾正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"我屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:03:21.000Z","msg":"排隊啦你"},{"pid":"f2bbe2da0485892de05b8eb352310da5719206f4","tid":585437,"uid":59869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"細路眼盲<br />\n大家覺得似唔似係呢條女?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/models/myphoto.php?id=2858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fmodels%2Fmyphoto.php%3Fid%3D2858&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSW3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=cc97bc8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/models/myphoto.php?id=2858</a>"},{"pid":"196e5da3dfac77da9e2bc7183db10c8c71f4df5b","tid":585437,"uid":50506,"